we can access a method and variable without creating object by adding Static keyword in the method.

Step 1:
Create a Parent class (below example:consider "Addition")

step 2:Create a method with keyword static.

step 3:Create the Main class and Main method.

step 4:Now Enter the Parentclass.methodname.(In the below example enter Parentclass.method)

Sample Program:
----------------

package selenium;

class Addition{

static void add(int a , int b){

int sum =  a +  b;

}
}

public class Statickeyword{

public static void main(String[]Args){

Addition.add(10, 15);

}
}

